  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Armenia: Strengthening the Integrity of Armenia&#x2019;s Criminal Justice Sector &#x2013; Phase II</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1) To strengthen the capacity of Armenian justice sector institutions for targeted anti-corruption reforms. 2) To increase alignment of organizational practices in combatting corruption and complex crimes with international standards and good practices.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Academy of Justice; Anti-Corruption Committee; Bureau of the Representative of the Republic of Armenia to the European Court of Human Rights; Courts (Specialized Anti-Corruption Court, district courts, Criminal Court of Appeals and Cassation Court); Prosecutor General&#x2019;s Office (Department for Confiscation of Property of Illicit Origin, Department for Combatting Corruption Crimes); Chamber of Advocates</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to support justice sector institutions in Armenia to become more effective and accountable .</narrative>
  </description>
